data.title: What is the Tour de France theme tune called?
data.meta_description:
Answer (1 of 2): I’m a Brit and don’t know which songs are used for coverage in other countries but there are two which immediately come to mind when thinking about our coverage.

One is by the German electronic pioneers and cycling fans Kraftwerk. It’s called, strangely enough, Tour de France an...
